comment: Gasol (MEM) makes incidental contact with Nowitzki (DAL) that does not affect his FOM.
Green (MEM) maintains legal guarding position and does not affect Williams' (DAL) RSBQ.
Randolph (MEM) is in a legal rebounding position and does not dislodge Williams (DAL).
Powell (DAL) maintains legal guarding position as he defends Randolph's (MEM) post move and shot attempt.
Allen (MEM) makes incidental contact with Williams's (DAL) arm that does not affect his RSBQ.
Pachulia (DAL) maintains legal guarding position as he defends Randolph's (MEM) post move.
Parsons (DAL) and Barnes (MEM) briefly engage and separate away from the ball.
After communicating with the Replay Center, the ruling on the court that the ball was last touched by Pachulia (DAL) prior to going OOB was confirmed.
Felton (DAL) sets the screen on Gasol (MEM) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Nowitzki (DAL) moves his pivot foot. The official is looking for any potential illegal contact and does not pick up the pivot foot.
Gasol (MEM) makes contact with Nowitzki's (DAL) body that affects his jump shot attempt.
Randolph (MEM) grabs the jersey of Pachulia (DAL), affecting his ability to retrieve the rebound.
Randolph (MEM) makes incidental contact with Pachulia's (DAL) face during rebounding.
Randolph (MEM) and Pachulia (DAL) briefly engage and separate during rebounding.
Nowitzki (DAL) maintains legal guarding position as he defends Gasol's (MEM) driving shot attempt. Gasol initiates the contact on the play.
Felton (DAL) sets the screen on Gasol (MEM) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Nowitzki (DAL) maintains legal guarding position as he defends Green's (MEM) driving shot attempt. Green jumps backwards into Nowitzki and initiates the contact on the play.
Green (MEM) makes contact with the ball before it has reached its apex and is still on its upward flight toward the basket.
LHH shows that Gasol (MEM) pushes Pachulia (DAL) affecting his ability to defend on the play.
Nowitzki (DAL) makes incidental contact with Randolph's (MEM) arm after the shot is released.
Barnes (MEM) makes contact with Williams's (DAL) arm that causes him to lose control of the ball.
L-SLA shows that Pachulia (DAL) maintains legal guarding position as he defends Gasol's (MEM) driving shot attempt.
Pachulia (DAL) maintains legal guarding position and makes incidental contact that does not affect Conley's (MEM) driving shot attempt.
Randolph (MEM) commits a take foul on Felton (DAL).
Felton (DAL) legally contests Conley's (MEM) jump shot attempt.
Conley's (MEM) FT attempt does not make contact with the rim and a violation is correctly called.
After communicating with the Replay Center, the ruling on the court that Conley was behind the three point line on his shot attempt was confirmed.
